Creation of table and text table
======================================

First Domain for Iitem ID- ZDITEMID:
----------------------------------------
- /nse11
- domain- ZDITEMID, click on create
- shortdescription Iteam id
- datatype (click on on search box and choose NUMC
- no. characters give 10
- click on check syntac and activate and save it as local object
-

Second Domain for Iitem Description- ZDITEMDES:
----------------------------------------
- /nse11
- domain- ZDITEMDESC, click on create
- shortdescription IteaM Description
- datatype (click on on search box and choose CHAR
- no. characters give 40
- click on check syntac and activate and save it as local object

First Dataelement for item domain-ZDEITEMID:
----------------------------------------
- click on datatype - ZDEITEMID
- click on create
- choose dataelement
- short description - item id
- in domain give ZDITEMID
- click on field label
- give item id in all 4 blocks
- click on syntac check and click on active and click on locla object

Second Dataelement for item domain-ZDEITEMIDesc:
----------------------------------------
- click on datatype - ZDEITEMIDESC
- click on create
- choose dataelement
- short description - item description
- in domain give ZDITEMIDESC
- click on field label
- give item Desc in all 4 blocks
- click on syntac check and click on active and click on locla object

Creation of primary table:
----------------------------------------
- ose11
- databasetable ZTITEM
- click on create
- short description: item table - Primary table
- choose delivery claass - C
- Databroswer - display/maintanance Allowed
- click on fields
-  Field     key  Initi           Dataelement   
 MANDT         <                   MANDT
 ITEM ID       <                   ZDEITEMID
- click on techical settings
- Data class - choose  APPL2
- Size category- 0
- click on save 
- click on back
- click on activete and save

Creation of texttable:
----------------------------------------
-ose11
- databasetable - ZTITEMT
- click on create
- short description: Item Details- Text table
- delivery class - C
- Databrowser - Display/Maintenance Allowed
- click on fields
-  Filed     key  Initi           Dataelement   
 MANDT         <                   MANDT
 SPRAS         <                   SPRAS
 ITEM ID       <                   ZDEITEMID
 ITEMSDSC                          ZDEITEMIDESC
- Click on activate and save as local object
- Click on technical setting and choose table is language-depndenet but not traansalate
- dataclass - APPL2
- Size category -0
- click on save
- click  on activate, click on save

Text Table - Assigning Relationship Between Primary Table and Text Table:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-  go to text table , click on foreign key
- give the name of check table- ZTITEM, CLICK ON create proposal
- Foregion key field type - choose key fields of a text table
- cardinality-  1: N
- click on copy
- click on activate

To check the relation:
----------------------------------------
- go to primary key table, clikc on goto , and click on text table

Text Table - Maintaining Text Into Primary Table and Text Table:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

- go to nse11, got to primary key table
- click on change mode
- click on utilities- table maintenance generator
- TALBE/VIEW -ZTITEM
-  autorization group - &N&
- Function group -ZTITEM
- Maintenancy type- one step
- click on find scrn number on top
- Maint.screen no  Overiew screen -1
- click on create and save

- go to nse11, go to text table
- TALBE/VIEW -ZTITEMT
-  autorization group - &N&
- Function group -ZTITEMT
- Maintenancy type- one step
- click on find scrn number on top
- Maint.screen no  Overiew screen -1
- click on create and save

- Now got to osm30, 
- table/view  -ZTITEM
- Click on new entries
 01 TEA
 02  COFFE
 03  MILK

- osm30,
- table/view ZTITEMT, CLICK on edit
- table/view  -ZTITEMT
- You will see logon laungue entries automatically 
- Click on new entries
-  de  1   TEE
-  de  2   KAFEE
-  DE  3   MILCH
-  click on save
-  you will see both the langueges now in the text teable

Search Help Creation Using Primary Table and Text Table:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- nse11 
- in serach helpt  ZSH_ITEMNO
- choose elementary search help 
- short description: search helpt for item number
- selection method:  ZTITEM
- Text table  ZTITEMT
- In the parameter section :
Search help parameter  IMP EXP Lpos Spos Sdis Dataeleemnnt
 ITEMID                 <    <   1   1
 ITEMDSC                <    <   2   2
- execute

Suppose i need the serach help in programe:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- nse38
- Programe - ZITEM_PRG
- click on create 
- title- Items Display Programe
- type - executable
- save
REPORT ZITEM_PRG.
PARAMETERS: p_item TYPE ZDEITEMID MATCHCODE OBJECT ZSH_ITEMNO.
- Click on active and run the programe
- click on selection text choose ddic reference and click on activate
  execute
- click on f4 help near itemid , you will see the text table


Check Table and Value Table Part1
----------------------------------------


Order Status table:
 Oder Number - N(10)
 Order status- C(1) - Y(Yes)/(No)

Order Vendor Details:
 Order Number - N(10)
 Vendor detaikls - c(1) - I(Internal), E(External)

- check table works at field level in foreign key
- se11
- database table ZORDSTATUS_28
- Short description Order status table
- Delivery class C
- Databrowseer/table view editing - display/maintenance allowed with restrictions
- click on Fields
-  Field     key  Initi           Dataelement   
 MANDT         <                   MANDT
 ONO           <                   ZDEONO
 OSTATHS                           ZDEOSTAT_28 (It will ask for to create dataelement

- click on yes
- data element- ZDEOSTAT_28
- short description- order status
- click on field label
- short   Ord.stat
- Medium  Order status
- Long     Order status
- Heading   Order status
- in domain -Zdordstat_28
- short description -= order status
- datay type CHAR
- NO OF CHAR -1
- click on value range
  fixed   short description
   y      Yes
   n       No
- click on activate
- now go to dataelement and activate
- now go to table and click on techincal setting
- data class - APPL2
- SIZE CATEGORY 0
- CLICK ON SAVE
- NOW got to back buttong and click on activate



